    <item>
      <title>关税担心华尔街的压力会加速减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/tariff-panic-on-wall-street-pressures-trump-to-speed-up-tax-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税使市场进入尾矿，总统越来越多地加快他为经济榨汁的主要提议：一项全面的税收法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/tariff-panic-on-wall-street-pressures-trump-to-speed-up-tax-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国绿党看到本周国防支出协议的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/german-greens-see-chance-for-defense-spending-deal-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的绿党准备在本周达成协议，这将为数千亿欧元的国防和基础设施支出铺平道路，与该国未来的下一任总理弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/german-greens-see-chance-for-defense-spending-deal-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 06:26:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杜特尔特（Duterte</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/philippines-says-ex-leader-duterte-arrested-after-icc-warrant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周末，罗德里戈·杜特尔特（Rodrigo Duterte）在他多年来的第一次海外旅行中召集了数千名在香港欢呼的菲律宾移民工人。周二返回马尼拉后，他加入了一个因违反国际法而被捕的前领导人俱乐部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/philippines-says-ex-leader-duterte-arrested-after-icc-warrant</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 03:17:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei签署执行法令，以支持阿根廷的IMF计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/argentina-s-milei-signs-executive-decree-to-back-imf-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈维尔·米利（Javier Milei）周一签署了一项紧急行政法令，要求在阿根廷与国际货币基金组织之间达成一项新协议，这表明员工级协议比以往任何时候都更近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/argentina-s-milei-signs-executive-decree-to-back-imf-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 00:31:12 GMT</pubDate>
